Class ActorTimeLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • movieproject.ActorTimeLine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<info.movito.themoviedbapi.model.people.PersonCredit>

    public class ActorTimeLine
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<info.movito.themoviedbapi.model.people.PersonCredit>
    ActorTimeLine is essentially a wrapper for the PersonCredits class that uses a TmdbMovies object to all the retrieval of additional categories of info, such as the revenue generated by a referenced by a film in an actor's PersonCredits.
    Since:
    7-7-2017
    Version:
    2
    Author:
    Pieter Holleman, Zachary Hern, Adam Slifco
